data.description: Enjoy to lake lifestyle of Lake Travis in this thoughtfully designed home nestled in the privately gated community of Windermere Oaks in Spicewood, Texas.  This home boasts an open concept design to entertain your guest with two bedrooms and two baths in the main house with a separate 1 bedroom guest apartment and living area that can be used for additional guests, office, or entertaining with a half bath attached to the two-car garage. As you approach the home, you will be greeted with many deer on the expansive double, tree-filled lot, landscaped, which sets the tranquil tone of comfort and elegance that awaits you. The main level features rich parquet wood floors throughout the living, kitchen, and bedroom. The exquisite island kitchen is perfect for meal prep or casual dining and features stainless appliances, high-end granite countertops, which provide a sleek updated look for this lake house. The primary bedroom is upstairs in order to take advantage of the large porch with incredible hill country views. Come take a look at this unique opportunity to own a slice of heaven.
